{
  "chapter": 42,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤在松花江畔小镇展开调查。他先到丁老大留下的巨型水缸中拜访神秘老人老山羊，得知李霞仍藏在镇上、两个大水缸原本成对，老山羊看穿他不是贾乐山却未点破，临别警告他小心狐狸精。接着陆小凤去唐可卿的\"不醉无归小酒家\"试探消息，唐可卿先是妩媚勾引，随即翻脸将他赶出门，原来她有虐待男人的怪癖。之后他在草药店遇到冷红儿，见她教训上门调戏的男人，冷红儿向他倾诉独居的寂寞与苦楚，两人互生好感，却在亲热之际被李神童撞破。李神童认出陆小凤真实身份，自称是蓝胡子安插在李霞身边的内应，告知要见李霞须先送箱子到银钩赌坊。陆小凤回到天长酒楼，发现楚楚早已准备将箱子运往赌坊，箱中装的是砖头——真正的黄金就是箱体本身。楚楚解释此计策的精妙，陆小凤虽感被骗却也佩服其手段，最终拒绝了楚楚的示好。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你上不上得来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "我上去干什么？我又不是司马光，我就算想要喝水，也用不着爬到这么样一个大水缸里去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你见过这么大的水缸没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你见过我没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "但我却好像见过你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你就是贾乐山贾大爷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你不是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "我不是贾乐山？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "绝不是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "那么我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "不管你是张三也好，是李四也好，我只知道你绝不是贾乐山，因为我以前见过那老王八羔子一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "我想请……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "李霞是个怪人，丁老大更怪，为了喜欢喝无根水，居然不惜卖地卖房子，花了两年多的功夫做成这么样两个大水缸，只为了夏天的时候接雨水喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "丁老大就是李霞以前的老公？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "现在李霞虽然不见了，却绝对没有离开这地方，我可以保证她一定还躲在镇上，你若想问我她躲在哪里，我也不知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "你怎么知道我是来打探这些事的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "难道你不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "你也已知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我不必知道，也不想知道，不管你是谁，都跟我一点关系也没有。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我觉得你这人还不讨厌，所以就带你到这里来，告诉你这些话，假如你还想打听什么别的事，你最好找别人去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "你说这样的水缸本来是有两个的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "还有一个呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "别的事，你什么都不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我已经老了，老得几乎连自己贵姓大名都忘了，镇上的年轻人很多，年轻的女孩子也很多，无论你打听什么消息，都应该问他们去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "你知道我不是贾乐山，知道我认得丁老大的女儿，所以我提起她的名字时，你一点也不意外，你甚至还知道李霞并没有走，可是你却口口声声的说什么你都不知道。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "listener_name": "老山羊",
      "text": "看来辛老二倒没有说错，你的确不该叫老山羊，你实在是条老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "老山羊",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你遇上我这条老狐狸倒不要紧，我只希望你莫要再遇上只狐狸精。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "听说你已经把天长酒楼买了下来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "这地方消息传得好快！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "这是个小地方，像你这样的大人物并不常见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "不醉无归，到这里喝酒的，难道都非醉不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "对，到这里来喝酒的，不醉都是乌龟。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "若是醉了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "醉了就是王八。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "所以到这里来喝酒的人，不做乌龟，就得做王八，这就难怪没有人敢上你的门了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "可是你已经上了我的门。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你明明已买下酒楼，却还要到这里来喝酒，你既不怕做乌龟，也不怕做王八，你这是为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "你猜我是为了什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "难道你为的是我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "只要你肯陪我喝酒，你要我醉也好，要我不醉也好，都由得你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "所以我要你做乌龟也好，做王八也好，你都答应？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "那只看你答不答应？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你总得先放开我的手，让我去拿酒给你。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "listener_name": "唐可卿",
      "text": "你这是干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我正想问你，你这是干什么？你把我看成什么样的人？你以为自己有几个臭钱，就可以随便欺负女人？告诉你，我这里只卖酒，不卖别的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ke_qing",
      "speaker_name": "唐可卿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "滚，你给我滚出去，下趟若是再敢上我的门，看我不一棍子打断你两条狗腿。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_nan_ke",
      "listener_name": "男客",
      "text": "你究竟是什么地方扭了筋？什么地方错了骨？你说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_ke",
      "speaker_name": "男客",
      "listener": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "listener_name": "冷红儿",
      "text": "我……我没有。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_nan_ke",
      "listener_name": "男客",
      "text": "那么你来干什么？是不是想来捏捏我的筋，松松我的骨？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你是不是也有病想来找我治治？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你究竟是来干什么的？为什么不说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "listener_name": "冷红儿",
      "text": "我为什么一定要说话？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "其实你不说我也知道，你心里一定认为我是个又冷又凶，又有毛病的女人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "listener_name": "冷红儿",
      "text": "我没有这么想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "listener_name": "冷红儿",
      "text": "你这是干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "也没有什么，我……我只不过觉得很难受。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "listener_name": "冷红儿",
      "text": "难受？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你是从外地来的，你不知道这里的男人都是些什么样的人，他们看我一个人住在这里，总是想尽了办法，要来欺负我、侮辱我。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我若被他们欺负了一次，以后就永远没法子做人了，因为别人非但不会怪他们，反而会说我招蜂引蝶，所以我只好作出那种冷冷冰冰的样子，可是每当夜深人静的时候，我又……又……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "其实我们以前并没有见过面，我本不该在一个陌生人面前说这种话的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "listener_name": "冷红儿",
      "text": "没关系，我也有很多心事，有时候我也想找个陌生人说给他听听。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你能不能说给我听？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "这酒还是我以前从外地带来的，我一直舍不得喝。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "每天晚上，我都要一个人喝一点酒，我的酒量并不好，可是我喝醉了才能睡得着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "冷红儿",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "有时候就算喝醉了也一样睡不着，那种时候我就跑出去，坐在冰河上，等着天亮，有一次我甚至还看见一头熊，至少我以为它是一头熊，它身上长满又粗又硬的黑毛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "两位千万不要停下来，这么精彩的好戏，我已经有很多年没看过了，你们只要肯让我再多看一下子，我明天一定请你们吃糖。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你可不能过来，我知道我打不过你，我知道你是什么人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你瞒得过别人，却瞒不过我，就算你再把胡子留多些也没用，我还是知道你是那个有四条眉毛的陆小凤。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "可是你只管放心，我绝不会揭穿这秘密的，因为我们本就是一条路上的人，我等你来已等了很久。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "你知道我会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "蓝胡子说过他一定会把你找来的，他说的话我一直很相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你一定想不到我会出卖我姐姐，替蓝胡子做奸细。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "但是我也并不太奇怪，像你这种人，还有什么事做不出的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "等你见过我那宝贝姐姐，你就知道我为什么要做这种事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "我要怎么样才能见到她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "只有一个法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "赶快把你带来的那些箱子送去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "你也不知道她躲在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我也不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李神童",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "除了白花花的银子，和黄澄澄的金子外，她简直已六亲不认。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_li_shen_tong",
      "listener_name": "李神童",
      "text": "你想不想挨揍？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你总算还记得回来，我还以为你已死在那个女人的小肚子上了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "这酒还是我特地带来的……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "快叫人送去，快！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "快把什么东西送去？送到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "快把箱子送到银钩赌坊去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "你们站在这里发什么呆？砖头又摔不疼，快装好送去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "送去？送到哪里？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "当然是送到银钩赌坊去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "你想用砖头去换人家的罗刹牌？你以为人家都是呆子？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "就因为那位陈姑娘一点都不呆，所以我才能把箱子就这么样送去，她若是识货的，看了这些箱子一定没话说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "别的箱子里装的也是砖头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "完全一样的砖头，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "不过怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "箱子里装的虽然是砖头，箱子却是用黄金打成的，我们带着这么多黄金走这么远的路，总不能不特别小心些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "我知道你一直在生我的气，我知道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "listener_name": "陆小凤",
      "text": "可是今天晚上，我绝不会再让你生气了，绝不会。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "listener_name": "楚楚",
      "text": "是什么事让你改变了主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
